description.p:
To this end, according to one functional aspect, the invention relates to a method for managing the transmission of the location of a first geo-tag able to communicate with a second geo-tag, the tags being classified into a plurality of respective categories, the first tag being associated with a first category, the method comprising the following steps in the first tag:
a. detecting proximity between the first tag (BAL1) and the second geo-tag (BAL2);
b. obtaining the category associated with the second tag (BAL2);
c. transmitting, to the second tag (BAL2), a request to transfer the management of the transmission of the location of the first tag, if the obtained category belongs to a second tag category.

According to one hardware aspect, the invention relates to a management entity for managing the transmission of the location of a first geo-tag able to communicate with a second geo-tag, the tags being classified into a plurality of respective categories, the first tag being associated with a first category, the entity comprising:
a. a detection module for detecting proximity between the first tag and a second geo-tag;
b. an obtainment module for obtaining the category associated with the second tag;
c. a transmission module able to transmit, to the second tag, a request to transfer the management of the transmission of the location of the first tag, if the obtained category belongs to a second tag category.
